        <Parent_String>garnitures (armor) [300206545], armors by function [300224810], armors (object groupings) [300226591], armor groupings [300241516], costume groupings [300210821], object groupings by specific context [300241512], object groupings [300241507], Object Groupings and Systems (hierarchy name) [300241489], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
